# Design System: Tokens

> **Scope**: Applies to all frontend source files. Governs color, typography, spacing, and shadow usage.
> **Full spec**: `docs/design-system/tokens.md`

## Color Rules

### MUST use CSS custom properties, never hardcode colors

```tsx
// GOOD
<div className="bg-[var(--accent)] text-[var(--accent-foreground)]">

// BAD — hardcoded hex
<div className="bg-[#0052FF] text-white">
```

### The Accent Gradient

The signature gradient (`var(--accent)` → `var(--accent-secondary)`) is the primary visual identity. Use it on:
- Primary buttons: `bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--accent)] to-[var(--accent-secondary)]`
- Featured badges and icon containers
- Text highlights: `.gradient-text` class
- Gradient borders on featured cards

### Inverted Sections

For dramatic contrast, use `bg-[var(--foreground)] text-[var(--background)]` with dot pattern texture.

## Typography Rules

### Font Assignment

| Role | CSS Variable | Class |
|:-----|:-------------|:------|
| Display headlines (h1/h2) | `--font-display` (Calistoga) | `font-display` |
| Body & UI | `--font-sans` (Inter) | `font-sans` (default) |
| Monospace labels | `--font-mono` (JetBrains Mono) | `font-mono` |

### Type Scale

- Hero headlines: `text-5xl` to `text-[5.25rem]`, tight leading (`leading-[1.05]`)
- Section headlines: `text-3xl` to `text-[3.25rem]`, `leading-[1.15]`
- Card titles: `text-lg` to `text-2xl`, `font-semibold`
- Body: `text-base` to `text-lg`, `leading-relaxed` (1.625+)
- Section labels: `text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.15em]`

### Gradient Text

Apply to the key word in headlines:

```tsx
<h2 className="font-display text-4xl">
  Headline with <span className="gradient-text">highlighted</span> word
</h2>
```

## Spacing Rules

- Section vertical padding: `py-28` to `py-44`
- Container: `mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6`
- Card padding: `p-6` to `p-10`
- Grid gaps: `gap-5` to `gap-8`

## Shadow Rules

| Context | Class |
|:--------|:------|
| Subtle lift | `shadow-sm` |
| Standard card | `shadow-md` |
| Elevated card | `shadow-lg` |
| Hero element | `shadow-xl` |
| Accent hover | Use inline: `shadow-[0_4px_14px_rgba(0,82,255,0.25)]` |

## Border Radius

- Buttons: `rounded-xl` (12px)
- Cards: `rounded-xl` or `rounded-2xl`
- Inputs: `rounded-lg` or `rounded-xl`
- Badges: `rounded-full`
